originalText.text: Working with JDATSG has been a remarkable experience! As an employee, I found their team to be supportive, professional, and dedicated to creating a positive work environment. I highly recommend JDATSG for both their outstanding services and employee-friendly culture!

originalText.text: As a PFE first, now a CE with JDA across 2 employment periods (2019-2020 and 8/21-present) I've had the privilege to make a lot of great new friends and see the quality delivered, first hand, of all the extremely talented Engineers on the JDA staff.  Great company to work for, twice!
